#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/data-papers.adoc:6
msgid "A data paper is a peer reviewed document describing a dataset, published in a peer reviewed journal. It takes effort to prepare, curate and describe data. Data papers provide recognition for this effort by means of a scholarly article."
msgstr ""

